    {
      "chinese": "經各原住民族人積極努力恢復說族語訴求，原民會於民國90年起對原住民語言陸續進行研討，及鼓勵族語創作、推廣、與研究，於民國94年會銜教育部共同頒訂「原住民語言書寫系統」，使原住民語言得以推動發展、資源挹注及扶助。",
      "ab": "Spuda sediq Tnpusu miyah meysa pbrnahan rmngaw ka kari sediq tnpusu, kndadax kngkwassan 2001 ciida wada kmdudul pprngaw, dmudul prana  matas mi qmqur smluhay kari sediq tnpusu ka yeynminhwey. Kngkwasan 2005 wada msupu Ciyawyupu pkla mi smalu “pnskraya pptasan kari sediq Tnpusu Taywan”, kiya mtduwa pprana muway hbangan mi pplkuh qqpahun nii.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2024/12/06/92b6d3f37382837e25202d6f596e8e4b.wav",
